text: Brachaciptera auricoma is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Lea in 1917. It is known from Australia.BioLib.cz - Brachaciptera auricoma. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Cerambycinae Category:Beetles described in 1917
